data.description: Absolutely fantastic house in the highly sought after Hampshire Neighborhood in St Charles.  The neighborhood has picturesque tree lined streets with sidewalks, ponds, and a community center with pool.  House is wonderful starting with a wide concrete driveway leading to oversized 2 car garage with extended workshop area.  The front porch is invitingly large with plenty of space for furniture and enjoying the quiet cul-de-sac, waving to neighbors and enjoying the fresh air.  Inside is unique with the main level boasting to a very large living/family room (please see floorplans for layout), kitchen has been updated with modern appliances and granite counters.  There is a separate dining area and arrival area off the garage.  Backyard has a large patio with a fenced in yard, perfect for large gatherings and enjoying the outdoors.  The upper level has 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Owners suite is huge with  plenty of closet space and private bathroom.  Owners have completed many upgrades including updating the Roof with a 30 plus year shingle, HVAC is 1 year old, Hot water heater is less than 2 years old, Windows and back patio door less than 1 year old, installed granite in kitchen, new floors on main level, and Tesla Solar Panels.  House will not last.
